  (str hindiTitle) (str `राष्‍ट्रीय मानसिक स्‍वास्‍थ्‍य और तंत्रिका-विज्ञान संस्‍थान, बंगलौर अधिनियम, 2012`)
  (str actYear) (str 2012)
  (str ministry) (str `Ministry of Health and Family Welfare`)
  (str department) (str `Department of Health and Family Welfare`)
  (str longTitle) (str `An Act to declare the institution known as the National Institute of Mental Health and NeuroSciences, Bangalore, to be an institution of national importance and to provide for its incorporation and for matters connected therewith.`)
